{"id":"816496dd-c47d-4c63-aac6-b18c4a2e6f46","name":"Detailed Realistic Real World RPG","description":"<p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/oGRKejoQSylQL_P-tUUGo.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/z0QFtOC-MPh4av7VMPMbN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/64_QEdgKcYzkAR5DC9Xef.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/pWnt_Gv2IGNbjXXkrAPOz.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wHUYYWMUhxZ1riVTYtoXa.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><strong>Have you ever wondered how life would've been if you were someone else Realistically? Well, Now you can be that someone else! But still Realistic. I also add a Dark Twist of the world, For more Realism, So no fluff, No fake hope</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>You can be rich</strong></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yCyQbGiSm193da9Rjz0lK.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>Or broke and poor</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kkmdBHGxnOswH1YaMO3rk.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XscaHf0KC5nSydJBsYO4T.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p></p><p><strong>The NPC response is hoped To be Direct And realistic, But because of the JLLM i don't know how to fix it.</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Trust me, This is the best you can find</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>So thank you, Enjoy</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>I Created this Bot because i was inspired by @Mayu0910, Because this is about Real life RPG, I created this bot because i found few flaws about Her bot.</strong></p><p><strong>So, Thank You Mayu0910.</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"DHoG_X15omhlt9NHFN5Qr.webp","creator":"Raiden Kazuku ","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["⛓️ Dominant","🪢 Scenario","📙 Philosophy","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":3742,"messages":156899,"created_at":"2025-08-25T13:19:47.174705+00:00"}